Package com.example.mainapplication.datainterface.caching

Interface StorageInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CacheAccess, MockCache, StorageAccess
    public interface StorageInterface
    The interface Storage interface is used to store data in the cache. The cache is used to store data that is used in the app.
    Author:
    Ryan Leska
